WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:03.166
&gt;&gt;ANNOUNCER: TODAY ON

00:00:03.166 --> 00:00:04.333
THE JOHN ANKERBERG SHOW:

00:00:04.333 --> 00:00:05.600
WHAT WILL HAPPEN TO YOU

00:00:05.600 --> 00:00:07.300
ONE MINUTE AFTER YOU DIE?

00:00:07.300 --> 00:00:09.533
STATISTICS TELL US:

00:00:09.533 --> 00:00:11.000
ONE HUNDRED AND SIX PEOPLE

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:13.266
DIE EVERY MINUTE. FIFTY-FIVE

00:00:13.266 --> 00:00:15.000
THOUSAND PEOPLE DIE EVERY DAY.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:17.467
FOUR-AND-A HALF MILLION PEOPLE

00:00:17.467 --> 00:00:19.667
DIE EVERY MONTH. AND FIFTY-SIX

00:00:19.667 --> 00:00:22.500
MILLION PEOPLE DIE EACH YEAR.

00:00:22.500 --> 00:00:23.834
IF YOU LIVE FOR SEVENTY

00:00:23.834 --> 00:00:25.667
YEARS, OVER YOUR LIFETIME,

00:00:25.667 --> 00:00:28.200
CLOSE TO FOUR BILLION PEOPLE

00:00:28.200 --> 00:00:30.133
WILL HAVE DIED ON EARTH.

00:00:30.133 --> 00:00:31.967
AND EVENTUALLY DEATH WILL

00:00:31.967 --> 00:00:33.533
COME TO YOU AND TO ME.

00:00:33.533 --> 00:00:35.533
NONE OF US WILL ESCAPE IT.

00:00:35.533 --> 00:00:37.633
WHAT DOES THE BIBLE SAY

00:00:37.633 --> 00:00:39.066
EACH OF US WILL EXPERIENCE

00:00:39.066 --> 00:00:41.033
ONE MINUTE AFTER WE DIE.

00:00:41.033 --> 00:00:44.066
MY GUEST TODAY IS THEOLOGIAN

00:00:44.066 --> 00:00:45.433
AND BEST-SELLING AUTHOR,

00:00:45.433 --> 00:00:47.467
DR. ERWIN LUTZER, SENIOR

00:00:47.467 --> 00:00:49.166
MINISTER OF MOODY CHURCH IN

00:00:49.166 --> 00:00:51.066
CHICAGO, ILLINOIS, WHO HAS

00:00:51.066 --> 00:00:52.233
WRITTEN THE BOOK,

00:00:52.233 --> 00:00:53.667
"ONE MINUTE AFTER YOU DIE."

00:00:53.667 --> 00:00:55.400
WE INVITE YOU TO JOIN US

00:00:55.400 --> 00:00:56.867
FOR THIS SPECIAL EDITION OF

00:00:56.867 --> 00:00:59.767
THE JOHN ANKERBERG SHOW.

00:01:02.500 --> 00:01:03.667
&gt;&gt;JOHN ANKERBERG: WELCOME TO

00:01:03.667 --> 00:01:04.834
OUR PROGRAM.

00:01:04.834 --> 00:01:06.000
I'M JOHN ANKERBERG.

00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:07.166
THANKS FOR JOINING ME TODAY.

00:01:07.166 --> 00:01:08.333
WE HAVE ONE OF THESE RARE

00:01:08.333 --> 00:01:09.667
TOPICS THAT APPLIES TO EVERY

00:01:09.667 --> 00:01:11.667
ONE OF YOU THAT IS WATCHING.

00:01:11.667 --> 00:01:13.367
WHETHER YOU'RE HERE IN

00:01:13.367 --> 00:01:15.033
AMERICA OR CANADA OR RUSSIA

00:01:15.033 --> 00:01:17.533
OR EUROPE OR INDIA OR AFRICA

00:01:17.533 --> 00:01:20.066
OR SOUTH AMERICA, THIS TOPIC

00:01:20.066 --> 00:01:22.667
APPLIES TO EVERYBODY THAT IS

00:01:22.667 --> 00:01:23.834
WATCHING. WE'RE GOING TO TALK

00:01:23.834 --> 00:01:28.333
ABOUT DEATH AND WHAT YOU WILL

00:01:28.333 --> 00:01:30.066
EXPERIENCE ONE MINUTE AFTER

00:01:30.066 --> 00:01:32.967
YOU DIE. AND MY GUEST TODAY

00:01:32.967 --> 00:01:35.433
IS MY GOOD FRIEND,

00:01:35.433 --> 00:01:36.600
DR. ERWIN LUTZER.

00:01:36.600 --> 00:01:37.934
HE IS THE PASTOR OF

00:01:37.934 --> 00:01:39.233
THE HISTORIC MOODY CHURCH

00:01:39.233 --> 00:01:40.400
IN CHICAGO, ILLINOIS.

00:01:40.400 --> 00:01:42.967
AND, ERWIN, WHY IS THIS

00:01:42.967 --> 00:01:44.333
SO IMPORTANT TO EVERYBODY

00:01:44.333 --> 00:01:45.500
THAT'S LISTENING?

00:01:45.500 --> 00:01:46.834
&gt;&gt;DR. ERWIN LUTZER: WELL,

00:01:46.834 --> 00:01:48.000
JOHN, FIRST OF ALL I WANT

00:01:48.000 --> 00:01:49.166
TO SAY WHAT A DELIGHT IT IS

00:01:49.166 --> 00:01:50.333
TO BE HERE TO DISCUSS THIS

00:01:50.333 --> 00:01:52.367
INCREDIBLY IMPORTANT TOPIC.

00:01:52.367 --> 00:01:54.900
AND WE WELCOME ALL

00:01:54.900 --> 00:01:56.066
THE PEOPLE WHO ARE LISTENING.

00:01:56.066 --> 00:01:57.633
BUT, YOU KNOW, THE BIBLE

00:01:57.633 --> 00:01:59.100
TEACHES THAT GOD ACTUALLY

00:01:59.100 --> 00:02:01.367
HAS PUT ETERNITY IN OUR

00:02:01.367 --> 00:02:04.333
HEARTS. I THINK ATHEISTS EVEN

00:02:04.333 --> 00:02:06.000
WHEN THEY COME TO DIE ARE

00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:07.834
WELL AWARE THAT THERE IS

00:02:07.834 --> 00:02:09.600
SOMETHING ON THE OTHER SIDE.

00:02:09.600 --> 00:02:12.000
AND THE BIBLE SAYS, "IT IS

00:02:12.000 --> 00:02:14.033
APPOINTED UNTO MAN ONCE TO

00:02:14.033 --> 00:02:16.133
DIE, AND AFTER THAT

00:02:16.133 --> 00:02:18.934
THE JUDGMENT." AND TRY AS

00:02:18.934 --> 00:02:21.600
WE MIGHT TO PUT DEATH OUT OF

00:02:21.600 --> 00:02:23.667
OUR MINDS, WHEN IT'S OUR TIME

00:02:23.667 --> 00:02:25.800
TO DIE I CAN ASSURE YOU

00:02:25.800 --> 00:02:27.600
THAT OUR MINDS WILL BE VERY

00:02:27.600 --> 00:02:29.734
FOCUSED ON WHAT LIES ON

00:02:29.734 --> 00:02:31.200
THE OTHER SIDE OF THE CURTAIN.

00:02:31.200 --> 00:02:32.900
&gt;&gt;ANKERBERG: YES. YOU WERE

00:02:32.900 --> 00:02:34.967
ASKED AS A PASTOR TO DO

00:02:34.967 --> 00:02:36.467
A FUNERAL, AND IT WAS

00:02:36.467 --> 00:02:37.633
A VERY KIND OF STRANGE

00:02:37.633 --> 00:02:40.066
CIRCUMSTANCE. TELL US

00:02:40.066 --> 00:02:41.233
ABOUT THAT.

00:02:41.233 --> 00:02:42.400
&gt;&gt;LUTZER: YES. WHAT HAPPENED

00:02:42.400 --> 00:02:43.567
IS, I RECEIVED A CALL FROM

00:02:43.567 --> 00:02:45.200
A FUNERAL HOME, AND THEY ASKED

00:02:45.200 --> 00:02:46.667
ME TO COME OVER AND TO SPEAK

00:02:46.667 --> 00:02:48.734
BRIEFLY. NOW, WHEN I GOT THERE

00:02:48.734 --> 00:02:51.433
THE SON WHOSE FATHER HAD DIED

00:02:51.433 --> 00:02:53.867
TOOK ME ASIDE AND SAID,

00:02:53.867 --> 00:02:55.667
"WE WANT YOU TO BE VERY

00:02:55.667 --> 00:02:57.200
BRIEF." AS A MATTER OF FACT,

00:02:57.200 --> 00:02:58.800
WHAT HE SAID IS, "NOTHING THAT

00:02:58.800 --> 00:03:01.300
YOU SAY WILL BE TOO SHORT."

00:03:01.300 --> 00:03:03.633
HE SAID, "WE DON'T BELIEVE

00:03:03.633 --> 00:03:05.233
IN GOD. MY FATHER DIDN'T

00:03:05.233 --> 00:03:06.734
BELIEVE IN GOD. WE ARE

00:03:06.734 --> 00:03:08.567
ATHEISTS. AND THE ONLY REASON

00:03:08.567 --> 00:03:09.967
YOU'RE HERE IS BECAUSE

00:03:09.967 --> 00:03:11.266
A RELATIVE THOUGHT THAT

00:03:11.266 --> 00:03:12.800
A MINISTER SHOULD BE

00:03:12.800 --> 00:03:14.800
PRESENT." SO I SAID,

00:03:14.800 --> 00:03:15.967
"I'M GOING TO MAKE

00:03:15.967 --> 00:03:17.133
AN AGREEMENT WITH YOU.

00:03:17.133 --> 00:03:18.300
I'M NOT GOING TO TALK ABOUT

00:03:18.300 --> 00:03:20.000
YOUR FATHER." BUT I SAID,

00:03:20.000 --> 00:03:21.467
"IN THE FEW MOMENTS THAT

00:03:21.467 --> 00:03:23.700
I AM GOING TO SPEAK, I'M GOING

00:03:23.700 --> 00:03:25.367
TO BE TALKING ABOUT JESUS

00:03:25.367 --> 00:03:27.266
CHRIST AND ETERNITY."

00:03:27.266 --> 00:03:29.000
WELL, WHAT COULD HE DO?

00:03:29.000 --> 00:03:31.066
HE HAD TO ALLOW ME TO DO THAT.

00:03:31.066 --> 00:03:33.934
BUT YOU KNOW, JOHN, JUST THINK

00:03:33.934 --> 00:03:35.633
OF WHAT THAT MAN WAS

00:03:35.633 --> 00:03:38.100
EXPERIENCING AFTER HIS DEATH.

00:03:38.100 --> 00:03:39.900
&gt;&gt;ANKERBERG: YES, WHILE YOU

00:03:39.900 --> 00:03:41.066
WERE PARKING THE CAR,

00:03:41.066 --> 00:03:42.233
WHILE YOU WERE MAKING

00:03:42.233 --> 00:03:43.400
THE ARRANGEMENTS, WHILE YOU

00:03:43.400 --> 00:03:44.567
WERE TALKING WITH THE FAMILY,

00:03:44.567 --> 00:03:46.033
THE MAN THAT WAS IN

00:03:46.033 --> 00:03:47.533
THE CASKET, ACCORDING TO

00:03:47.533 --> 00:03:48.700
THE BIBLE, WAS WHAT?

00:03:48.700 --> 00:03:50.700
&gt;&gt;LUTZER: YOU KNOW, WE'RE

00:03:50.700 --> 00:03:51.934
GOING TO BE LOOKING AT THIS

00:03:51.934 --> 00:03:53.367
IN MUCH MORE DETAIL, BUT IN

00:03:53.367 --> 00:03:54.767
THE SIXTEENTH CHAPTER OF

00:03:54.767 --> 00:03:57.200
LUKE, JESUS TELLS A STORY.

00:03:57.200 --> 00:04:00.200
AND I DON'T BELIEVE THAT

00:04:00.200 --> 00:04:02.100
IT WAS A PARABLE. I THINK

00:04:02.100 --> 00:04:03.266
IT'S AN ACTUAL STORY.

00:04:03.266 --> 00:04:05.400
HE TELLS THE STORY OF A RICH

00:04:05.400 --> 00:04:07.633
MAN WHO DIED AND ALSO A POOR

00:04:07.633 --> 00:04:10.400
MAN WHO DIED. AND THE POINT

00:04:10.400 --> 00:04:11.800
THAT JESUS WAS MAKING IS

00:04:11.800 --> 00:04:13.066
NOT THAT RICHES LEAD YOU

00:04:13.066 --> 00:04:15.800
TO HELL; BUT IT IS TRUE THAT

00:04:15.800 --> 00:04:17.767
THE RICH MAN ENDED UP IN WHAT

00:04:17.767 --> 00:04:19.600
IS CALLED HADES. AND WE'RE

00:04:19.600 --> 00:04:20.767
GOING TO HAVE TO DISCUSS

00:04:20.767 --> 00:04:22.633
THAT ON THIS SHOW. AND IT SAYS

00:04:22.633 --> 00:04:25.066
ALSO THAT THE POOR MAN,

00:04:25.066 --> 00:04:26.333
WHOSE NAME WAS LAZARUS,

00:04:26.333 --> 00:04:28.633
WAS IN ABRAHAM'S BOSOM.

00:04:28.633 --> 00:04:31.266
THE QUESTION IS: WHAT WAS

00:04:31.266 --> 00:04:32.667
THE RICH MAN EXPERIENCING?

00:04:32.667 --> 00:04:35.333
WELL, AS THE BIBLE CLEARLY

00:04:35.333 --> 00:04:37.266
INDICATES, HE WAS IN A STATE

00:04:37.266 --> 00:04:39.800
OF PAIN, OF TORMENT, AND

00:04:39.800 --> 00:04:42.367
HE WAS GOING THROUGH ALL OF

00:04:42.367 --> 00:04:43.567
THESE EXPERIENCES.

00:04:43.567 --> 00:04:45.767
AND I BELIEVE THAT, THAT RICH

00:04:45.767 --> 00:04:48.200
MAN IN CHICAGO, WHILE I SPOKE

00:04:48.200 --> 00:04:50.100
BRIEFLY AND THEN THERE WAS

00:04:50.100 --> 00:04:51.266
A RATHER LONG EULOGY

00:04:51.266 --> 00:04:53.600
ABOUT HIM AND ALL OF

00:04:53.600 --> 00:04:55.734
HIS ACCOMPLISHMENTS, HE WAS

00:04:55.734 --> 00:04:58.633
ALSO IN HADES, IN THAT PLACE

00:04:58.633 --> 00:05:00.767
THAT IS DESCRIBED AS ONE OF

00:05:00.767 --> 00:05:02.734
ABANDONMENT AND TORMENT.

00:05:02.734 --> 00:05:04.400
AND RIGHT FROM THE BEGINNING

00:05:04.400 --> 00:05:05.767
WE HAVE TO MAKE THIS VERY

00:05:05.767 --> 00:05:07.800
CLEAR: THAT THERE IS A BIG

00:05:07.800 --> 00:05:09.166
DIFFERENCE BETWEEN WHAT

00:05:09.166 --> 00:05:10.700
YOU SEE WHEN SOMEONE DIES AND

00:05:10.700 --> 00:05:13.400
YOU SEE THEIR LIFELESS BODY,

00:05:13.400 --> 00:05:15.100
AND WHAT THEY ARE

00:05:15.100 --> 00:05:17.166
EXPERIENCING. BECAUSE AFTER

00:05:17.166 --> 00:05:19.233
THEY'VE DIED, WHAT THEY FIND

00:05:19.233 --> 00:05:20.967
IS THEY ARE IN AN ENTIRELY

00:05:20.967 --> 00:05:23.767
DIFFERENT WORLD, A DIFFERENT

00:05:23.767 --> 00:05:25.834
REALM. AND DEATH IS NOT

00:05:25.834 --> 00:05:27.667
A POSITIVE EXPERIENCE

00:05:27.667 --> 00:05:28.834
FOR EVERYONE.

00:05:28.834 --> 00:05:30.000
&gt;&gt;ANKERBERG: YES, AND YOU

00:05:30.000 --> 00:05:31.166
SAY THAT NOT EVERYBODY'S

00:05:31.166 --> 00:05:32.333
GOING TO HAVE THE SAME KIND

00:05:32.333 --> 00:05:34.000
OF EXPERIENCE. YOU HAVE

00:05:34.000 --> 00:05:35.266
THOSE WHO KNOW THE LORD

00:05:35.266 --> 00:05:36.600
HAVE ONE KIND OF EXPERIENCE

00:05:36.600 --> 00:05:38.166
AND THOSE THAT DO NOT KNOW

00:05:38.166 --> 00:05:39.333
THE LORD HAVE ANOTHER.

00:05:39.333 --> 00:05:40.500
EXPLAIN THAT.

00:05:40.500 --> 00:05:41.667
&gt;&gt;LUTZER: WELL, FIRST OF

00:05:41.667 --> 00:05:42.834
ALL, LET ME SAY THAT THOSE

00:05:42.834 --> 00:05:44.000
WHO KNOW JESUS CHRIST AS

00:05:44.000 --> 00:05:46.033
SAVIOR, THEY WILL BE IN

00:05:46.033 --> 00:05:47.200
HIS PRESENCE. THEY WILL BE

00:05:47.200 --> 00:05:49.233
BLESSED. WE CAN CALL THAT

00:05:49.233 --> 00:05:50.700
PARADISE; WE CAN CALL THAT

00:05:50.700 --> 00:05:52.667
HEAVEN; AND THEY HAVE THAT

00:05:52.667 --> 00:05:54.633
ASSURANCE. AND ON THESE

00:05:54.633 --> 00:05:55.967
PROGRAMS WE'RE GOING TO BE

00:05:55.967 --> 00:05:57.400
TALKING ABOUT THAT ASSURANCE

00:05:57.400 --> 00:05:59.066
THAT THEY HAVE. BECAUSE,

00:05:59.066 --> 00:06:01.734
AFTER ALL, JESUS IS THE ONLY

00:06:01.734 --> 00:06:05.000
SAVIOR. NOW, WE HAVE MANY

00:06:05.000 --> 00:06:07.033
PROPHETS AND GURUS WHO TELL

00:06:07.033 --> 00:06:09.000
US HOW TO LIVE, BUT NOBODY

00:06:09.000 --> 00:06:11.767
EXCEPT JESUS CAN ACTUALLY

00:06:11.767 --> 00:06:13.834
WIPE AWAY OUR SIN AND

00:06:13.834 --> 00:06:15.367
PREPARE US FOR HEAVEN.

00:06:15.367 --> 00:06:16.834
ON THE OTHER SIDE, OF COURSE,

00:06:16.834 --> 00:06:18.734
ARE THOSE WHO ARE GOING TO BE

00:06:18.734 --> 00:06:20.667
IN TORMENT. AND EVEN HADES

00:06:20.667 --> 00:06:22.934
THAT WE'RE GOING TO BE TALKING

00:06:22.934 --> 00:06:25.000
ABOUT IS NOT YET HELL.

00:06:25.000 --> 00:06:27.467
SO IT'S VERY IMPORTANT FOR

00:06:27.467 --> 00:06:29.033
PEOPLE TO UNDERSTAND-AND

00:06:29.033 --> 00:06:31.767
THIS IS CRITICAL-THERE IS NO

00:06:31.767 --> 00:06:34.066
MIDDLE GROUND. THERE IS

00:06:34.066 --> 00:06:36.200
NO PLACE WHERE YOU SAY,

00:06:36.200 --> 00:06:37.867
"WELL, I'M NOT GOOD ENOUGH

00:06:37.867 --> 00:06:39.667
FOR HEAVEN, BUT I'M TOO GOOD

00:06:39.667 --> 00:06:42.033
FOR HELL, SO THERE'S A MIDDLE

00:06:42.033 --> 00:06:43.767
PLACE." NO, THERE ISN'T.

00:06:43.767 --> 00:06:47.133
IT IS ONLY HEAVEN OR HADES,

00:06:47.133 --> 00:06:49.266
WHICH LATER ON IS THROWN

00:06:49.266 --> 00:06:50.867
INTO HELL, A VERY

00:06:50.867 --> 00:06:52.233
STARK CONTRAST.

00:06:52.233 --> 00:06:53.667
&gt;&gt;ANKERBERG: YES, I LOVED

00:06:53.667 --> 00:06:54.834
WHAT YOU SAID AT

00:06:54.834 --> 00:06:56.000
THE BEGINNING HERE, THAT

00:06:56.000 --> 00:06:57.166
PEOPLE, GOD HAS PUT A DESIRE

00:06:57.166 --> 00:07:00.367
IN THEIR HEARTS OF ETERNITY,

00:07:00.367 --> 00:07:02.567
AND THEY HAVE A DESIRE TO

00:07:02.567 --> 00:07:05.467
KNOW WHAT'S BEYOND DEATH,

00:07:05.467 --> 00:07:07.300
TO PEEK BEHIND THE CURTAIN OF

00:07:07.300 --> 00:07:10.567
DEATH. AND THERE ARE A COUPLE

00:07:10.567 --> 00:07:11.967
OF AREAS THAT OUR SOCIETY

00:07:11.967 --> 00:07:14.367
AND NATIONS AROUND THE WORLD,

00:07:14.367 --> 00:07:15.533
PEOPLE IN DIFFERENT NATIONS

00:07:15.533 --> 00:07:16.767
AROUND THE WORLD, HAVE TRIED

00:07:16.767 --> 00:07:20.467
TO USE TO GET INFORMATION

00:07:20.467 --> 00:07:22.033
ABOUT WHAT'S GOING TO HAPPEN

00:07:22.033 --> 00:07:24.166
AFTER DEATH. ONE OF THOSE

00:07:24.166 --> 00:07:26.734
HAS BEEN CHANNELING TO TRY

00:07:26.734 --> 00:07:28.967
TO GET A GLIMPSE OF WHAT

00:07:28.967 --> 00:07:30.133
LIES BEYOND THE GRAVE.

00:07:30.133 --> 00:07:32.367
WHAT DOES THE BIBLE SAY

00:07:32.367 --> 00:07:33.834
ABOUT CHANNELING?

00:07:33.834 --> 00:07:35.633
&gt;&gt;LUTZER: YOU KNOW,

00:07:35.633 --> 00:07:37.000
CHANNELING IS WHEN YOU GO TO

00:07:37.000 --> 00:07:38.700
A MEDIUM WHO SUPPOSEDLY

00:07:38.700 --> 00:07:40.467
CONNECTS YOU WITH PEOPLE WHO

00:07:40.467 --> 00:07:42.734
HAVE DIED. AND SOMETIMES

00:07:42.734 --> 00:07:44.100
THERE HAVE EVEN BEEN SHOWS ON

00:07:44.100 --> 00:07:45.567
TELEVISION WHERE YOU GO TO

00:07:45.567 --> 00:07:46.800
THIS PERSON AND HE SAYS,

00:07:46.800 --> 00:07:48.667
"I CAN CONTACT YOUR MOTHER,

00:07:48.667 --> 00:07:51.066
YOUR FATHER, AND WE'LL

00:07:51.066 --> 00:07:53.500
TALK." THE BIBLE FORBIDS ALL

00:07:53.500 --> 00:07:56.200
OF THAT. HERE IN THE UNITED

00:07:56.200 --> 00:07:57.433
STATES THERE WAS A BISHOP

00:07:57.433 --> 00:07:58.633
WHO DID NOT BELIEVE

00:07:58.633 --> 00:08:01.000
THE BIBLE, AND HE DECIDED

00:08:01.000 --> 00:08:02.734
TO TRY TO CONTACT HIS SON

00:08:02.734 --> 00:08:04.266
WHO HAD COMMITTED SUICIDE.

00:08:04.266 --> 00:08:06.734
SO THE BISHOP, PIKE WAS HIS

00:08:06.734 --> 00:08:08.633
NAME, HE WENT TO A MEDIUM,

00:08:08.633 --> 00:08:11.567
AND THE MEDIUM PURPORTEDLY

00:08:11.567 --> 00:08:13.533
CONNECTED HIM WITH HIS BOY.

00:08:13.533 --> 00:08:15.900
AND HE ASKED HIS SON, AMONG

00:08:15.900 --> 00:08:17.700
OTHER THINGS, "DO YOU HEAR

00:08:17.700 --> 00:08:19.200
ABOUT JESUS ON THE OTHER

00:08:19.200 --> 00:08:21.367
SIDE?" AND THE SON SAID,

00:08:21.367 --> 00:08:22.934
"NO, WE DON'T HEAR A LOT

00:08:22.934 --> 00:08:24.567
ABOUT JESUS ON THE OTHER

00:08:24.567 --> 00:08:27.000
SIDE." JOHN, FROM MY HEART

00:08:27.000 --> 00:08:28.266
TO YOURS AND TO THE MANY

00:08:28.266 --> 00:08:29.433
PEOPLE WHO ARE LISTENING,

00:08:29.433 --> 00:08:31.567
IF, WHEN YOU DIE, YOU'RE IN

00:08:31.567 --> 00:08:32.867
A PLACE WHERE YOU DON'T HEAR

00:08:32.867 --> 00:08:34.567
MUCH ABOUT JESUS, YOU'RE IN

00:08:34.567 --> 00:08:37.433
DEEP TROUBLE. THE BIBLE

00:08:37.433 --> 00:08:38.734
FORBIDS CHANNELING,

00:08:38.734 --> 00:08:39.900
AND I'LL TELL YOU WHY.

00:08:39.900 --> 00:08:41.934
IT SPEAKS ABOUT FAMILIAR

00:08:41.934 --> 00:08:44.367
SPIRITS; THAT IS, THERE ARE

00:08:44.367 --> 00:08:47.033
DEMONS WHO KNOW ALL ABOUT

00:08:47.033 --> 00:08:49.166
US. AND IF THAT CHANNELER,

00:08:49.166 --> 00:08:50.967
THAT MEDIUM, IS ABLE TO

00:08:50.967 --> 00:08:52.300
CONNECT WITH ONE OF THOSE

00:08:52.300 --> 00:08:54.533
DEMONS, THE DEMONS SPEAK AND

00:08:54.533 --> 00:08:56.800
THEY SUPPLY INFORMATION.

00:08:56.800 --> 00:09:00.300
