THE OTHER SIDE. IN FACT,

00:09:05.467 --> 00:09:07.200
IN THE SCRIPTURE WE READ

00:09:07.200 --> 00:09:09.200
IN ISAIAH, "AND WHEN

00:09:09.200 --> 00:09:10.633
THEY SAY TO YOU, 'CONSULT

00:09:10.633 --> 00:09:12.300
THE MEDIUMS AND THE SPIRITISTS

00:09:12.300 --> 00:09:14.500
WHO WHISPER AND MUTTER.

00:09:14.500 --> 00:09:17.066
SHOULD NOT A PEOPLE CONSULT

