ON THE OTHER SIDE.

00:09:32.767 --> 00:09:34.200
&gt;&gt;ANKERBERG: AND MANY OTHER

00:09:34.200 --> 00:09:36.066
PEOPLE HAVE TRIED DIFFERENT

00:09:36.066 --> 00:09:37.900
WAYS, SUCH AS REINCARNATION,

00:09:37.900 --> 00:09:39.767
AND NOW WE'VE HAD THIS

00:09:39.767 --> 00:09:41.500
PHENOMENON OF A LOT OF

00:09:41.500 --> 00:09:42.867
PEOPLE HAVING NEAR-DEATH

00:09:42.867 --> 00:09:45.000
EXPERIENCES. YOU'VE GOT MANY

00:09:45.000 --> 00:09:46.400
NEW AGE WRITERS AND

00:09:46.400 --> 00:09:47.700
PHILOSOPHERS, PEOPLE IN

00:09:47.700 --> 00:09:49.000
HOLLYWOOD EVEN MAKING MOVIES

