WHAT DOES THE BIBLE HAVE TO

00:09:55.900 --> 00:09:57.367
SAY ABOUT REINCARNATION AND

00:09:57.367 --> 00:09:59.900
THEN NEAR-DEATH EXPERIENCES?

00:09:59.900 --> 00:10:01.400
&gt;&gt;LUTZER: WELL, LET'S TALK

00:10:01.400 --> 00:10:02.767
ABOUT REINCARNATION.

00:10:02.767 --> 00:10:03.934
I HAVE TO TELL YOU ABOUT

00:10:03.934 --> 00:10:05.266
A STORY, JOHN, THAT I HAD.

00:10:05.266 --> 00:10:06.433
I WAS SITTING ON A,

00:10:06.433 --> 00:10:08.633
ON AN AIRPLANE AND NEXT TO ME

00:10:08.633 --> 00:10:09.934
WAS A WOMAN BY THE NAME OF

00:10:09.934 --> 00:10:12.100
SHIRLEY. AND WHEN SHE FOUND

00:10:12.100 --> 00:10:13.867
OUT I WAS A PASTOR SHE SAID,

00:10:13.867 --> 00:10:15.367
"YOU'RE SO FORTUNATE; BECAUSE

00:10:15.367 --> 00:10:16.834
I'D LIKE TO BE ABLE TO PREACH

00:10:16.834 --> 00:10:18.367
TO PEOPLE AND TELL THEM ABOUT

00:10:18.367 --> 00:10:20.333
MY EXPERIENCES AND EVEN

00:10:20.333 --> 00:10:21.600
BRING HEALING TO THEM.

00:10:21.600 --> 00:10:23.467
AND FURTHERMORE," SHE SAID,

00:10:23.467 --> 00:10:25.000
"I CAN PROVE REINCARNATION."

00:10:25.000 --> 00:10:27.200
I SAID, "TELL ME MORE."

00:10:27.200 --> 00:10:29.300
SHE SAID, "EVEN WHEN I WAS

00:10:29.300 --> 00:10:31.166
A CHILD I HAD VISIONS AND

00:10:31.166 --> 00:10:34.100
DREAMS ABOUT A HOME IN

00:10:34.100 --> 00:10:36.500
VERMONT HERE IN THE UNITED

00:10:36.500 --> 00:10:37.900
STATES, THAT I'D NEVER BEEN

00:10:37.900 --> 00:10:40.934
TO. AND AS AN ADULT I VISITED

00:10:40.934 --> 00:10:42.767
THE HOME AND I REALIZED IT

00:10:42.767 --> 00:10:45.734
WAS EXACTLY AS THOSE VISIONS

00:10:45.734 --> 00:10:47.633
AND DREAMS INDICATED."

00:10:47.633 --> 00:10:49.767
NOW, I'M SITTING RIGHT NEXT

00:10:49.767 --> 00:10:50.934
TO HER, SO I SMILED AND

00:10:50.934 --> 00:10:52.333
I SAID TO HER, "SHIRLEY,

00:10:52.333 --> 00:10:53.834
I WANT TO TELL YOU SOMETHING.

00:10:53.834 --> 00:10:55.967
THERE'S NO SUCH THING AS

00:10:55.967 --> 00:10:57.834
A TRANSMIGRATION OF SOULS.

00:10:57.834 --> 00:10:59.767
THERE'S NO EVIDENCE IN

00:10:59.767 --> 00:11:01.900
THE BIBLE FOR REINCARNATION.

00:11:01.900 --> 00:11:03.900
BUT," I SAID, "THERE IS

00:11:03.900 --> 00:11:06.367
EVIDENCE OF THE TRANSMIGRATION

00:11:06.367 --> 00:11:08.533
OF DEMONS." I SAID,

00:11:08.533 --> 00:11:10.200
"THE INFORMATION THAT

00:11:10.200 --> 00:11:11.367
YOU ARE GETTING IS FROM

00:11:11.367 --> 00:11:13.000
A DEMONIC SPIRIT, AN EVIL

00:11:13.000 --> 00:11:15.100
SPIRIT WHO OBVIOUSLY KNOWS

00:11:15.100 --> 00:11:16.633
ABOUT THIS HOUSE IN VERMONT

00:11:16.633 --> 00:11:18.200
AND IS COMMUNICATING THIS

00:11:18.200 --> 00:11:19.467
INFORMATION TO YOU."

00:11:19.467 --> 00:11:21.700
AND SHE SAID, "OH NO!"

00:11:21.700 --> 00:11:24.166
SHE SAID, "I DO CONNECT WITH

00:11:24.166 --> 00:11:25.533
SPIRITS, BUT I RECEIVE

00:11:25.533 --> 00:11:27.500
NO INFORMATION FROM EVIL

00:11:27.500 --> 00:11:30.066
SPIRITS." I SAID, "TELL ME,

00:11:30.066 --> 00:11:31.266
HOW DO YOU TELL

00:11:31.266 --> 00:11:33.033
THE DIFFERENCE?" AND, JOHN,

00:11:33.033 --> 00:11:34.667
SHE SAID, "I RECEIVE ONLY

00:11:34.667 --> 00:11:37.500
THOSE SPIRITS THAT COME TO ME

00:11:37.500 --> 00:11:40.633
CLOTHED IN LIGHT."

00:11:40.633 --> 00:11:42.066
WELL, YOU PROBABLY ALREADY

00:11:42.066 --> 00:11:43.266
KNOW THE VERSE OF SCRIPTURE

00:11:43.266 --> 00:11:44.467
THAT I SHARED WITH HER,

00:11:44.467 --> 00:11:46.433
SECOND CORINTHIANS 11, WHERE

00:11:46.433 --> 00:11:48.066
THE APOSTLE PAUL SAYS THAT

00:11:48.066 --> 00:11:51.400
"SATAN HIMSELF IS TRANSFORMED

00:11:51.400 --> 00:11:54.266
INTO AN ANGEL OF LIGHT."

00:11:54.266 --> 00:11:56.700
AND I NEED TO SAY IT WITH

00:11:56.700 --> 00:11:58.900
EMPHASIS, THAT MUCH THAT

00:11:58.900 --> 00:12:00.166
WE HEAR TODAY ABOUT

00:12:00.166 --> 00:12:02.500
ENLIGHTENMENT IS ACTUALLY

00:12:02.500 --> 00:12:04.066
FROM THE DEMONIC WORLD.

00:12:04.066 --> 00:12:07.033
REINCARNATION IS NOT A WAY

00:12:07.033 --> 00:12:08.533
TO FIND OUT WHAT HAPPENS ON

00:12:08.533 --> 00:12:10.600
THE OTHER SIDE. NOW,

00:12:10.600 --> 00:12:12.100
YOU ALSO MENTIONED NEAR-DEATH

00:12:12.100 --> 00:12:13.333
EXPERIENCES.

