THEY ARE, AND THEN GIVE SOME

00:13:43.934 --> 00:13:45.500
ILLUSTRATIONS, AND THEN,

00:13:45.500 --> 00:13:46.667
WHAT DOES THE BIBLE SAY?

00:13:46.667 --> 00:13:48.166
&gt;&gt;LUTZER: THIS IS

00:13:48.166 --> 00:13:49.567
AN INCREDIBLY IMPORTANT TOPIC,

00:13:49.567 --> 00:13:51.133
BECAUSE I BELIEVE THAT THERE

00:13:51.133 --> 00:13:52.734
IS LOTS OF DECEPTION GOING

00:13:52.734 --> 00:13:53.900
ON WHEN IT COMES TO

00:13:53.900 --> 00:13:55.066
NEAR-DEATH EXPERIENCES.

00:13:55.066 --> 00:13:57.066
A NEAR-DEATH EXPERIENCE IS

00:13:57.066 --> 00:13:58.967
WHERE SOMEBODY IS ABOUT TO

00:13:58.967 --> 00:14:00.667
DIE, AND THEY MAY ACTUALLY

00:14:00.667 --> 00:14:04.100
DIE, AT LEAST THEORETICALLY,

00:14:04.100 --> 00:14:05.900
AND THEN THEY COME BACK TO

00:14:05.900 --> 00:14:07.934
LIFE. SO THEN THEY CAN TELL,

00:14:07.934 --> 00:14:10.233
SUPPOSEDLY, WHAT LIES ON

00:14:10.233 --> 00:14:11.400
THE OTHER SIDE.

00:14:11.400 --> 00:14:14.467
BUT THE PROBLEM IS, DO THEY

00:14:14.467 --> 00:14:15.967
HAVE ACCURATE INFORMATION?

00:14:15.967 --> 00:14:18.100
FOR EXAMPLE THERE'S A WOMAN

00:14:18.100 --> 00:14:19.433
BY THE NAME OF BETTY EADIE

00:14:19.433 --> 00:14:20.867
THAT WROTE A BOOK ENTITLED

00:14:20.867 --> 00:14:22.400
"EMBRACED BY THE LIGHT."

00:14:22.400 --> 00:14:24.166
SHE APPARENTLY HAD

00:14:24.166 --> 00:14:25.367
A NEAR-DEATH EXPERIENCE,

00:14:25.367 --> 00:14:27.367
CAME BACK AND SAID THAT

00:14:27.367 --> 00:14:29.200
SHE MET JESUS, AND THERE IS

00:14:29.200 --> 00:14:31.367
NO JUDGMENT AND EVERYONE CAN

00:14:31.367 --> 00:14:34.633
GO INTO THE OTHER SIDE WITHOUT

00:14:34.633 --> 00:14:37.633
ANY REGRETS. I REMEMBER

00:14:37.633 --> 00:14:39.200
A WOMAN WHO SAID THE VERY

00:14:39.200 --> 00:14:40.367
SAME THING TO ME.

00:14:40.367 --> 00:14:41.633
SHE SAID, "I ALMOST DIED.

00:14:41.633 --> 00:14:44.467
I DIED. I CAME BACK TO LIFE.

00:14:44.467 --> 00:14:46.700
JESUS, DURING THAT PERIOD OF

00:14:46.700 --> 00:14:48.300
TIME WHERE I WAS DEAD,

00:14:48.300 --> 00:14:50.166
TOOK ME BY THE HAND AND SAID,

00:14:50.166 --> 00:14:51.600
'HERE'S A BUDDHIST PATH;

00:14:51.600 --> 00:14:53.800
HERE'S AN ISLAMIC PATH;

00:14:53.800 --> 00:14:55.333
HERE'S A HINDU PATH;

00:14:55.333 --> 00:14:57.400
HERE'S A CHRISTIAN PATH.

00:14:57.400 --> 00:14:59.467
BUT, JUST LIKE SPOKES IN

00:14:59.467 --> 00:15:01.767
A WHEEL, THEY ALL LEAD TO

00:15:01.767 --> 00:15:04.300
THE HUB CALLED HEAVEN."

00:15:04.300 --> 00:15:06.133
WELL, OF COURSE, I TRIED TO

00:15:06.133 --> 00:15:07.567
HELP HER TO SEE THAT SHE WAS

00:15:07.567 --> 00:15:09.266
BEING DECEIVED, BECAUSE

00:15:09.266 --> 00:15:11.467
WE ALREADY MENTIONED IN THIS

00:15:11.467 --> 00:15:13.300
PROGRAM HOW SATAN TRANSFORMS

00:15:13.300 --> 00:15:15.467
HIMSELF TO AN ANGEL OF

00:15:15.467 --> 00:15:17.300
LIGHT, AND THERE IS NOTHING

00:15:17.300 --> 00:15:19.033
THAT THE DEVIL WOULD WANT

00:15:19.033 --> 00:15:21.000
MORE THAN TO MAKE US THINK

00:15:21.000 --> 00:15:22.800
THAT DEATH IS THE SAME

00:15:22.800 --> 00:15:24.266
EXPERIENCE FOR EVERYONE,

00:15:24.266 --> 00:15:25.934
A POSITIVE EXPERIENCE.

00:15:25.934 --> 00:15:29.667
WELL, IT IS NOT. BECAUSE

00:15:29.667 --> 00:15:31.567
JESUS SAID THESE WORDS,

00:15:31.567 --> 00:15:33.734
"I AM THE WAY, THE TRUTH AND

00:15:33.734 --> 00:15:36.166
THE LIFE. NO MAN COMES

00:15:36.166 --> 00:15:39.467
TO THE FATHER BUT BY ME."

00:15:39.467 --> 00:15:41.667
IN OTHER WORDS, YOU CAN'T

00:15:41.667 --> 00:15:43.333
GET TO THE FATHER WITHOUT

00:15:43.333 --> 00:15:45.166
JESUS CHRIST, AND THERE ARE

00:15:45.166 --> 00:15:46.900
POWERFUL REASONS WHY THAT IS

00:15:46.900 --> 00:15:48.200
THE CASE.

