&gt;&gt;ANKERBERG: WE'VE ALSO,

00:15:49.367 --> 00:15:50.867
BOTH OF US HAVE KNOWN

00:15:50.867 --> 00:15:53.166
A HEART DOCTOR.

00:15:53.166 --> 00:15:54.867
I'VE HAD HIM ON THE PROGRAM,

00:15:54.867 --> 00:15:57.100
DR. MAURICE RAWLINGS, WHO

00:15:57.100 --> 00:16:00.133
WAS NOT A CHRISTIAN AND WAS

00:16:00.133 --> 00:16:01.834
WORKING ON PATIENTS WHO HAD

00:16:01.834 --> 00:16:03.000
THESE NEAR-DEATH EXPERIENCES

00:16:03.000 --> 00:16:04.166
WHILE THEY WERE ON

00:16:04.166 --> 00:16:05.333
THE TREADMILL. THEY WOULD DIE

00:16:05.333 --> 00:16:06.500
AND HE WOULD RESUSCITATE THEM.

00:16:06.500 --> 00:16:07.667
AND ONE GUY, WHILE HE WAS

00:16:07.667 --> 00:16:08.834
DYING, SAID, "DOCTOR, DOCTOR,

00:16:08.834 --> 00:16:10.000
YOU'VE GOT TO SAVE ME,

00:16:10.000 --> 00:16:11.166
I'M IN HELL." HE SAYS,

00:16:11.166 --> 00:16:12.333
YOU KNOW, "KEEP YOUR HELL

00:16:12.333 --> 00:16:13.500
TO YOURSELF. I'M TRYING

00:16:13.500 --> 00:16:14.667
TO SAVE YOUR LIFE."

00:16:14.667 --> 00:16:16.333
AND HE CAME BACK EVERY TIME,

00:16:16.333 --> 00:16:17.767
AND HE, WHEN HE WOULD BE

00:16:17.767 --> 00:16:20.333
RESUSCITATED, SAID, "DOCTOR

00:16:20.333 --> 00:16:21.567
YOU'VE GOT TO PRAY FOR ME."

00:16:21.567 --> 00:16:22.734
SO HE MADE UP A PRAYER, AND

00:16:22.734 --> 00:16:25.567
HE SAID, "OKAY, DEAR JESUS,

00:16:25.567 --> 00:16:27.500
I'M A SINNER, YOU KNOW,

00:16:27.500 --> 00:16:29.600
I'M PUTTING ALL MY TRUST

00:16:29.600 --> 00:16:31.834
IN YOU. FORGIVE ME. HELP ME

00:16:31.834 --> 00:16:34.400
TO LIVE. IF YOU DO, I'M ON

00:16:34.400 --> 00:16:35.567
THE HOOK TO YOU."

00:16:35.567 --> 00:16:37.834
AND THE GUY STILL HAD THESE

00:16:37.834 --> 00:16:39.533
NEAR-DEATH EXPERIENCES, BUT

00:16:39.533 --> 00:16:41.100
NOW ALL OF A SUDDEN HE HAD

00:16:41.100 --> 00:16:43.667
PEACE. AND WE HAD AN AUDIENCE

00:16:43.667 --> 00:16:45.500
AT THAT TIME, AND THE GUY

00:16:45.500 --> 00:16:47.000
THAT, THAT HAD HAPPENED TO

00:16:47.000 --> 00:16:48.533
WAS SITTING IN THE AUDIENCE.

00:16:48.533 --> 00:16:51.567
HE CATALOGED OVER 300 HELL

00:16:51.567 --> 00:16:54.700
EXPERIENCES AT THAT TIME AND

00:16:54.700 --> 00:16:56.333
WROTE THEM INTO A BOOK.

00:16:56.333 --> 00:16:58.700
SO WHEN PEOPLE TALK ABOUT

00:16:58.700 --> 00:16:59.967
NEAR-DEATH EXPERIENCES,

00:16:59.967 --> 00:17:01.467
IF THEY'RE GOING TO TAKE

00:17:01.467 --> 00:17:02.633
A COUNT OF ALL OF

00:17:02.633 --> 00:17:03.800
THE INFORMATION THAT'S

00:17:03.800 --> 00:17:05.500
AVAILABLE, WHAT DO YOU DO

00:17:05.500 --> 00:17:07.133
WITH THESE PEOPLE THAT

00:17:07.133 --> 00:17:08.300
END UP IN HELL?

00:17:08.300 --> 00:17:09.467
&gt;&gt;LUTZER: WELL, EXACTLY.

00:17:09.467 --> 00:17:11.000
AND, JOHN, YOU'VE JUST GIVEN

00:17:11.000 --> 00:17:12.266
SOME POWERFUL INFORMATION.

00:17:12.266 --> 00:17:14.667
THE FACT IS THAT THERE CAN

00:17:14.667 --> 00:17:15.867
BE MUCH DECEPTION HERE,

00:17:15.867 --> 00:17:17.633
BECAUSE NOT EVERYBODY HAS

00:17:17.633 --> 00:17:19.166
THAT POSITIVE EXPERIENCE OF

00:17:19.166 --> 00:17:21.867
LIGHT. THERE INDEED MAY BE

00:17:21.867 --> 00:17:24.633
TIMES WHEN PEOPLE ARE

00:17:24.633 --> 00:17:26.300
IN TORMENT. AS A MATTER

00:17:26.300 --> 00:17:27.467
OF FACT, THE BIBLE TEACHES

00:17:27.467 --> 00:17:28.633
THAT. YOU KNOW, RECENTLY

00:17:28.633 --> 00:17:29.800
I WAS SPEAKING AT AN EVENT,

00:17:29.800 --> 00:17:32.400
AND A MAN CAME TO ME AND SAID

00:17:32.400 --> 00:17:33.867
THAT HIS MOTHER WAS NOT

00:17:33.867 --> 00:17:35.700
A BELIEVER. IN FACT, SHE WAS

00:17:35.700 --> 00:17:37.166
VERY MUCH OPPOSED TO

00:17:37.166 --> 00:17:38.333
THE CHRISTIAN FAITH.

00:17:38.333 --> 00:17:40.934
AND AS SHE WAS DYING SHE SAID,

00:17:40.934 --> 00:17:43.800
"GOD, HELP ME! I AM BURNING

00:17:43.800 --> 00:17:47.500
IN FLAMES." SO IF YOU WANT

00:17:47.500 --> 00:17:48.767
TO USE NEAR-DEATH EXPERIENCES,

00:17:48.767 --> 00:17:50.266
WE HAVE TO AT LEAST HAVE

00:17:50.266 --> 00:17:51.433
SOME BALANCE.

00:17:51.433 --> 00:17:53.567
BUT MY CONTENTION IS THIS:

00:17:53.567 --> 00:17:55.433
RATHER THAN DISCUSSING

00:17:55.433 --> 00:17:57.433
THE EXPERIENCE THAT PEOPLE HAD

00:17:57.433 --> 00:18:00.967
NEAR DEATH, IT'S MUCH BETTER

00:18:00.967 --> 00:18:04.200
IF WE TAKE AS AN AUTHORITY

00:18:04.200 --> 00:18:05.467
SOMEBODY WHO ACTUALLY

00:18:05.467 --> 00:18:08.934
WAS DEAD, AND WAS PUT IN

00:18:08.934 --> 00:18:11.400
THE GRAVE, AND DID RISE FROM

00:18:11.400 --> 00:18:13.900
THE GRAVE, AND HE'S THE ONE

00:18:13.900 --> 00:18:15.266
WHO CAN SPEAK WITH AUTHORITY.

00:18:15.266 --> 00:18:17.300
I LOVE THE WORDS OF SCRIPTURE.

00:18:17.300 --> 00:18:19.367
JESUS SAID IN REVELATION 1:18,

00:18:19.367 --> 00:18:22.767
"I AM HE THAT LIVETH

00:18:22.767 --> 00:18:24.633
AND WAS DEAD AND AM ALIVE

00:18:24.633 --> 00:18:26.967
FOREVERMORE, AND I HAVE

00:18:26.967 --> 00:18:29.166
THE KEYS OF DEATH AND OF

00:18:29.166 --> 00:18:33.000
HADES." JOHN, AT THE END OF

00:18:33.000 --> 00:18:35.400
THE DAY WHAT WE MUST ALWAYS

00:18:35.400 --> 00:18:37.767
RECOGNIZE IS THAT OUR

00:18:37.767 --> 00:18:39.266
RELATIONSHIP WITH JESUS

00:18:39.266 --> 00:18:41.567
CHRIST DETERMINES OUR

00:18:41.567 --> 00:18:43.800
DESTINY. HE'S THE ONE WHO HAS

00:18:43.800 --> 00:18:46.166
THE KEY OF DEATH AND OF HADES.

00:18:46.166 --> 00:18:48.633
AND HE'S THE ONE THAT

00:18:48.633 --> 00:18:49.934
SUPERVISES; HE'S THE ONE

00:18:49.934 --> 00:18:51.533
WHO OPENS DOORS AND CLOSES

00:18:51.533 --> 00:18:54.033
DOORS. SO OUR RELATIONSHIP

00:18:54.033 --> 00:18:55.633
WITH HIM IS INCREDIBLY

00:18:55.633 --> 00:18:56.800
IMPORTANT.

00:18:56.800 --> 00:18:58.667
&gt;&gt;ANKERBERG: NOW, LET'S USE

00:18:58.667 --> 00:19:00.200
THE BIBLE AS AN AUTHORITY

00:19:00.200 --> 00:19:01.734
AND LET'S USE THE OLD

00:19:01.734 --> 00:19:02.900
TESTAMENT AND THE NEW

00:19:02.900 --> 00:19:04.433
TESTAMENT. TALK ABOUT

00:19:04.433 --> 00:19:07.100
WHAT THE WORD "SHEOL" MEANS

00:19:07.100 --> 00:19:08.533
IN THE OLD TESTAMENT.

00:19:08.533 --> 00:19:09.867
&gt;&gt;LUTZER: THE WORD "SHEOL"

00:19:09.867 --> 00:19:11.333
OCCURS IN THE OLD TESTAMENT

00:19:11.333 --> 00:19:14.200
SIXTY-FIVE TIMES. THIRTY-ONE

00:19:14.200 --> 00:19:16.233
TIMES IT IS TRANSLATED "HELL";

00:19:16.233 --> 00:19:18.333
THE OTHER THIRTY-ONE TIMES IT

00:19:18.333 --> 00:19:19.934
IS TRANSLATED "THE GRAVE";

00:19:19.934 --> 00:19:22.333
AND THREE TIMES "THE PIT".

00:19:22.333 --> 00:19:24.567
NOW, BECAUSE OF THE FACT

00:19:24.567 --> 00:19:25.867
THAT IT IS TRANSLATED

00:19:25.867 --> 00:19:27.133
DIFFERENTLY, THERE COULD BE

00:19:27.133 --> 00:19:29.000
SOME CONFUSION. BUT WHEN

00:19:29.000 --> 00:19:30.300
YOU LOOK AT ALL OF THE TEXTS,

00:19:30.300 --> 00:19:31.834
YOU RECOGNIZE THAT HADES

00:19:31.834 --> 00:19:34.266
ACTUALLY IS THE SHADOWY WORLD,

00:19:34.266 --> 00:19:36.200
IF I CAN PUT IT THAT WAY,

00:19:36.200 --> 00:19:38.767
WHERE DEPARTED SPIRITS GO.

00:19:38.767 --> 00:19:40.767
NOW, THERE ARE SOME PEOPLE

00:19:40.767 --> 00:19:41.967
WHO BELIEVE THAT HADES IS

00:19:41.967 --> 00:19:43.467
NOTHING MORE THAN THE GRAVE.

00:19:43.467 --> 00:19:45.700
BUT THERE IS IN HEBREW

00:19:45.700 --> 00:19:47.266
A WORD FOR GRAVE.

00:19:47.266 --> 00:19:49.700
WHAT IT MEANS IS MORE THAN

00:19:49.700 --> 00:19:51.633
THE GRAVE, BECAUSE IT IS

00:19:51.633 --> 00:19:53.400
A PLACE THAT WELCOMES PEOPLE,

00:19:53.400 --> 00:19:54.600
ACCORDING TO THE OLD

00:19:54.600 --> 00:19:56.200
TESTAMENT; AND IT IS THERE

00:19:56.200 --> 00:19:58.166
WHERE WE FIND THAT PEOPLE

00:19:58.166 --> 00:19:59.967
COME AND THEY ARE FULLY

00:19:59.967 --> 00:20:02.200
CONSCIOUS. NOW, THE OTHER

00:20:02.200 --> 00:20:03.367
THING THAT'S IMPORTANT IS

00:20:03.367 --> 00:20:04.533
THAT IT MUST HAVE TWO

00:20:04.533 --> 00:20:06.433
COMPARTMENTS, BECAUSE ON

00:20:06.433 --> 00:20:07.667
THE ONE HAND YOU HAVE

00:20:07.667 --> 00:20:08.934
JACOB WHO GOES TO SHEOL.

00:20:08.934 --> 00:20:10.266
YOU HAVE THE RIGHTEOUS;

00:20:10.266 --> 00:20:11.633
YOU HAVE THE UNRIGHTEOUS;

00:20:11.633 --> 00:20:12.867
THEY ALL GO TO SHEOL.

00:20:12.867 --> 00:20:14.600
AND I THINK THAT THE RABBIS

00:20:14.600 --> 00:20:16.300
IN ANCIENT TIMES WERE

00:20:16.300 --> 00:20:18.567
CORRECT WHEN THEY SAID THAT

00:20:18.567 --> 00:20:21.600
SHEOL HAS TWO COMPARTMENTS.

00:20:21.600 --> 00:20:23.000
AND WHEN YOU GET TO THE NEW

00:20:23.000 --> 00:20:24.834
TESTAMENT I BELIEVE THAT

00:20:24.834 --> 00:20:26.133
JESUS CHRIST CONFIRMS THAT.

00:20:26.133 --> 00:20:28.000
&gt;&gt;ANKERBERG: YEAH, LET ME

00:20:28.000 --> 00:20:30.100
READ THE STORY THAT JESUS GAVE

00:20:30.100 --> 00:20:34.100
TO US ABOUT SHEOL, THIS IS

00:20:34.100 --> 00:20:36.400
A REAL STORY. IN LUKE 16

00:20:36.400 --> 00:20:39.166
IT'S TALKING ABOUT THE RICH

00:20:39.166 --> 00:20:40.934
MAN AND LAZARUS. JESUS SAYS,

00:20:40.934 --> 00:20:42.300
"NOW THE POOR MAN

00:20:42.300 --> 00:20:43.800
[THAT'S LAZARUS] DIED AND

00:20:43.800 --> 00:20:45.867
WAS CARRIED AWAY BY THE ANGELS

00:20:45.867 --> 00:20:47.100
TO ABRAHAM'S BOSOM."

00:20:47.100 --> 00:20:48.467
EXPLAIN THAT.

00:20:48.467 --> 00:20:49.633
"AND THE RICH MAN ALSO DIED

00:20:49.633 --> 00:20:51.100
AND WAS BURIED.

00:20:51.100 --> 00:20:53.333
AND THE RICH MAN IN HADES,

00:20:53.333 --> 00:20:56.166
HE LIFTED UP HIS EYES, BEING

00:20:56.166 --> 00:20:58.767
IN TORMENT, AND SAW ABRAHAM

00:20:58.767 --> 00:21:01.066
FAR AWAY AND LAZARUS IN HIS

00:21:01.066 --> 00:21:02.467
BOSOM. AND HE CRIED OUT

00:21:02.467 --> 00:21:04.300
AND SAID, 'FATHER ABRAHAM,

00:21:04.300 --> 00:21:07.734
HAVE MERCY ON ME AND SEND

00:21:07.734 --> 00:21:10.533
LAZARUS SO THAT HE MAY DIP

00:21:10.533 --> 00:21:11.700
THE TIP OF HIS FINGER IN

00:21:11.700 --> 00:21:13.834
WATER AND COOL OFF MY TONGUE;

00:21:13.834 --> 00:21:17.066
FOR I AM IN AGONY IN THIS

00:21:17.066 --> 00:21:18.767
FLAME.'" NOW, THIS IS JESUS

00:21:18.767 --> 00:21:20.333
TALKING. "BUT ABRAHAM SAID,

00:21:20.333 --> 00:21:23.233
'CHILD, REMEMBER THAT DURING

00:21:23.233 --> 00:21:24.667
YOUR LIFE YOU RECEIVED

00:21:24.667 --> 00:21:26.567
YOUR GOOD THINGS AND LIKEWISE

00:21:26.567 --> 00:21:29.033
LAZARUS, BAD THINGS.

00:21:29.033 --> 00:21:31.133
BUT NOW HE IS BEING

00:21:31.133 --> 00:21:32.300
COMFORTED HERE AND YOU ARE

00:21:32.300 --> 00:21:34.100
IN AGONY.'" AND THEN HE SAID,

00:21:34.100 --> 00:21:35.400
"'BESIDES ALL THIS, BETWEEN

00:21:35.400 --> 00:21:36.967
US AND YOU THERE IS A GREAT

00:21:36.967 --> 00:21:39.000
CHASM FIXED SO THAT THOSE

00:21:39.000 --> 00:21:40.367
WHO WISH TO COME OVER FROM

00:21:40.367 --> 00:21:41.900
HERE TO YOU WILL NOT BE

00:21:41.900 --> 00:21:43.800
ABLE, AND THAT NONE MAY

00:21:43.800 --> 00:21:45.533
CROSS OVER FROM THERE TO US.'

00:21:45.533 --> 00:21:48.500
AND HE SAID, 'THEN I BEG YOU,

00:21:48.500 --> 00:21:49.667
FATHER, THAT YOU SEND HIM

00:21:49.667 --> 00:21:50.834
TO MY FATHER'S HOUSE,

00:21:50.834 --> 00:21:52.000
FOR I HAVE FIVE BROTHERS,

00:21:52.000 --> 00:21:54.033
IN ORDER THAT HE MAY WARN

00:21:54.033 --> 00:21:56.166
THEM SO THAT THEY WILL NOT

00:21:56.166 --> 00:21:58.300
ALSO COME TO THIS PLACE OF

00:21:58.300 --> 00:22:00.367
TORMENT.' BUT ABRAHAM SAID,

00:22:00.367 --> 00:22:02.166
'THEY HAVE MOSES AND

00:22:02.166 --> 00:22:04.266
THE PROPHETS, LET THEM HEAR

00:22:04.266 --> 00:22:05.667
THEM.' BUT HE SAID, 'NO,

00:22:05.667 --> 00:22:07.767
FATHER ABRAHAM! BUT IF SOMEONE

00:22:07.767 --> 00:22:09.567
GOES TO THEM FROM THE DEAD,

00:22:09.567 --> 00:22:11.200
THEN THEY WILL REPENT.'

00:22:11.200 --> 00:22:12.767
BUT HE SAID TO THEM,

00:22:12.767 --> 00:22:14.400
'IF THEY DO NOT LISTEN

00:22:14.400 --> 00:22:15.834
TO MOSES AND THE PROPHETS

00:22:15.834 --> 00:22:17.800
THEY WILL NOT BE PERSUADED

00:22:17.800 --> 00:22:20.100
EVEN IF SOMEONE RISES FROM

00:22:20.100 --> 00:22:22.033
THE DEAD.'" ERWIN, EXPLAIN

00:22:22.033 --> 00:22:23.633
WHAT JESUS IS TEACHING HERE

00:22:23.633 --> 00:22:24.800
IN THIS STORY.

00:22:24.800 --> 00:22:26.133
&gt;&gt;LUTZER: JOHN, THIS IS

00:22:26.133 --> 00:22:27.734
A VERY SOBERING STORY, AND

00:22:27.734 --> 00:22:30.100
EVERYONE SHOULD LISTEN VERY

00:22:30.100 --> 00:22:31.367
CAREFULLY. AND I'M SO GLAD

00:22:31.367 --> 00:22:32.533
THAT YOU READ IT.

00:22:32.533 --> 00:22:33.700
BUT NOTICE THIS: FIRST OF

00:22:33.700 --> 00:22:34.867
ALL, THE MAN IS FULLY

00:22:34.867 --> 00:22:36.300
CONSCIOUS. I MEAN,

00:22:36.300 --> 00:22:38.166
HE CAN THINK; HE CAN FEEL;

00:22:38.166 --> 00:22:40.300
HE CAN SPEAK. ALL OF

00:22:40.300 --> 00:22:41.967
HIS SENSES ARE WORKING.

00:22:41.967 --> 00:22:43.834
AND HE'S IN TORMENT AND

00:22:43.834 --> 00:22:45.000
HE WANTS SOME WATER.

00:22:45.000 --> 00:22:46.400
AND THE MOST SOBERING

00:22:46.400 --> 00:22:47.767
THOUGHT THAT COULD EVER

00:22:47.767 --> 00:22:49.333
CROSS OUR MINDS TODAY IS

00:22:49.333 --> 00:22:52.367
THAT NOW, 2000 YEARS LATER,

00:22:52.367 --> 00:22:55.000
HE STILL DOES NOT HAVE

00:22:55.000 --> 00:22:57.967
HIS DRINK OF WATER. HADES IS

00:22:57.967 --> 00:22:59.600
GOING TO BE A PLACE OF TORMENT

00:22:59.600 --> 00:23:02.066
AS HE MENTIONED. THE OTHER

00:23:02.066 --> 00:23:03.300
THING ABOUT IT IS, YOU'LL

00:23:03.300 --> 00:23:04.667
NOTICE THAT HIS ETERNITY WAS

00:23:04.667 --> 00:23:06.900
FIXED. HE ASKED THE QUESTION

00:23:06.900 --> 00:23:08.066
AS TO WHETHER OR NOT

00:23:08.066 --> 00:23:09.300
HE COULDN'T PASS THIS GULF

00:23:09.300 --> 00:23:10.800
AND WHETHER OR NOT

00:23:10.800 --> 00:23:12.500
LAZARUS WOULD BE ABLE TO BRING

00:23:12.500 --> 00:23:13.667
HIM SOME WATER. AND ABRAHAM

00:23:13.667 --> 00:23:15.166
CLARIFIED, "NO, BETWEEN US

00:23:15.166 --> 00:23:16.400
THERE'S A GULF FIXED AND

00:23:16.400 --> 00:23:18.800
YOU CAN'T COME TO US AND

00:23:18.800 --> 00:23:20.200
WE CAN'T COME TO YOU."

00:23:20.200 --> 00:23:21.800
DO YOU REMEMBER DANTE WHEN

00:23:21.800 --> 00:23:23.133
HE WROTE HIS BOOK ABOUT

00:23:23.133 --> 00:23:25.667
HELL? ACROSS THE DOOR OF HELL

00:23:25.667 --> 00:23:26.834
HE SAID IS WRITTEN "ABANDON

00:23:26.834 --> 00:23:32.300
ALL HOPE, YE WHO ENTER HERE."

00:23:32.300 --> 00:23:33.700
NOW, ANOTHER THING, VERY

00:23:33.700 --> 00:23:35.767
QUICKLY; I THINK THAT, THAT

00:23:35.767 --> 00:23:37.367
MAN IN HADES KNEW THAT

00:23:37.367 --> 00:23:38.533
HIS SENTENCE WAS JUST.

00:23:38.533 --> 00:23:40.433
YOU'LL NOTICE THAT

00:23:40.433 --> 00:23:41.633
HE DOESN'T COMPLAIN AND SAY

00:23:41.633 --> 00:23:43.200
THAT "IT'S UNFAIR THAT

00:23:43.200 --> 00:23:44.834
I'M HERE." BUT, MOST

00:23:44.834 --> 00:23:47.200
IMPORTANTLY, HE KNEW EXACTLY

00:23:47.200 --> 00:23:49.133
WHAT HE SHOULD HAVE DONE

00:23:49.133 --> 00:23:50.300
TO AVOID THIS PLACE.

00:23:50.300 --> 00:23:52.367
HE SAID, "GO BACK AND TELL

00:23:52.367 --> 00:23:53.800
MY BROTHERS THAT THEY MIGHT

00:23:53.800 --> 00:23:55.900
REPENT SO THAT THEY WILL NOT

00:23:55.900 --> 00:23:57.500
COME TO THIS SAME PLACE OF

00:23:57.500 --> 00:24:00.467
TORMENT." SO THERE HE IS.

00:24:00.467 --> 00:24:02.400
AND MORE SOBERING, AND

00:24:02.400 --> 00:24:04.066
I'M SURE THAT WE'LL HAVE TO

00:24:04.066 --> 00:24:05.300
DISCUSS THIS ON ANOTHER

00:24:05.300 --> 00:24:08.066
SHOW, IS THE FACT THAT HADES

00:24:08.066 --> 00:24:10.734
AT THE END OF TIME IS THROWN

00:24:10.734 --> 00:24:15.266
INTO HELL. SO HADES IS NOT YET

00:24:15.266 --> 00:24:18.734
THE FINAL HELL, BUT STILL IS

00:24:18.734 --> 00:24:20.467
A PLACE OF TORMENT.

